/ Los Angeles Times; Photo, His two latest are "Cyrano de Bergerac," top, in 
which he woos Anne Brochet ... ; Photo, ... and "Green Card," above, in which 
he enters into a marriage of convenience with Andie MacDowell. 
</P>
